## Sample API Call (cURL) 
```
curl --request GET \
  --url {{ $env.WEBHOOK_URL }} \
  --data '{
  "image_url":"{{ $env.WEBHOOK_URL }}",
  "Requirement":"extract the details from the image",
  "properties": {
        "PAN Number": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "Name": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "Date of Birth": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "Valid": {
          "type": "boolean"
        }
      }
}'
```

## Sample Output
```
{
  "result": "{\"Date of Birth\":\"23/11/1974\",\"Name\":\"RAHUL GUPTA\",\"PAN Number\":\"ABCDE1234F\",\"Valid\":true}"
}
```
